        <title>Pika AI 推出音频驱动视频生成模型：6 秒生成超真实表情视频</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/pika-ai-%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%9F%B3%E9%A2%91%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B6-%E7%A7%92%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%B6%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/</link>
